<br>
What keeps our damage over time down?<br>
Aggro<br>
Mana Cost<br>
<br>
Fixing those two things IN OUR SPELLS would make our damage over time go up without more downtime.  Lowering mana cost by 10% or more on our spells would make our spells use less mana thus we could cast more with less downtime.  Lowering the base aggro or making concussion lower level and not a quest would help with aggro (or both).<br>
